summary: A sizable and homely nordic tomb refurbished into house at the crossroads of Dawnstar, Whiterun and Winterhold underneath a frigid coating of heavy snow with warmth and comfort on the inside.
descriptionHtml:
Reasonable size of a house (not a shack or a mansion)
Has all the amenities you will need or want
3 mannequins
9 shield racks
12 weapon racks
Cooking area/fireplace, beds, alchemy, and enchanting are in the first room
Smithing, wood chopping, display area are in the second
Plenty of chests and the like inside as well.
There is also a follower in the backroom.
author: Nonstron
